  <brief_title>3-midline-ports Cholecystectomy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Three Ports Placed in the Line Alba of the Abdomen (3-midline-ports Technique): an Alternative Approach for Laparoscopic Cholecystectomy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
